channel.title: [317] Fufuscape [317] Need Development Team
channel.description:
Hi my name is Rip1129 and I am currently creating a server I am very experienced in coding and etc. But right now I am currently looking for a development team such as other coders and people who know what they are doing in a server!! My website is fufuscape.webs.com if you want check it out the pics you see in the website is currently pics from the old server I updated fufuscape to a better version! I am currently adding a staff and donator zone!
What I am looking for in my team! 3-5 people People who can code People who I can trust with editing the website People who can take care of server and edit it when needed during my absents People who are trustworthy People who know what they are doing!! Some one who can host the server when need
If you are interested my email is rip1129@yahoo.com All staff will be automatic administrators and if one of them can host the server then they would be co-owner
